3.plot: Walter is sucked into Shayne's evil plan. Randy and Cliff have fisticuffs. Viv almost discovers Irene's twisted secret. Mike sees something horrible.

4.title: Chapter Four
4.plot: Cliff presses assault charges against Randy, who is bailed out and then kidnapped by old friend, Lyle, a sleazy pimp and porno director. Mike breaks up with Walter. Viv seeks information on Janet from Apartment Manager Mr. Hakopian who asks her to marry him. Debbie adopts "Oscar,' a stray cat.

5.title: Chapter Five
5.plot: Lyle hooks Randy on heroin and starts pimping him out to creepy men, then kidnaps Debbie. Mike and Walter get new boyfriends. Cliff gets sexually harassed by his boss, Nanette. Ondria, a practicing witch, puts a love spell on Cliff. Cliff falls in love with Nanette but she screams when he shows her his penis. Irene's captive sister stages a coup.

6.title: Chapter Six

7.title: Chapter Seven
7.plot: Time travel is implied. Irene seems to turn into Lotty at one point. Shayne commits his second murder.
